<div class="prose">
    <p>There are many ways to participate in our mission of combining faith and technology to serve those in need. Whether you have time, talents, or treasures to share, your contribution makes a difference.</p>
    
    <section id="donate" style="margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0;">
        <h2>Donate</h2>
        
        <div class="card" style="background: var(--parchment);">
            <h3>Financial Support</h3>
            <p>Your financial gifts enable us to maintain and expand our technological infrastructure while serving more families in need.</p>
            
            <h4>Where Your Money Goes:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>40% - Direct aid (food, shelter, medical assistance)</li>
                <li>25% - Technology development and maintenance</li>
                <li>20% - Volunteer coordination and training</li>
                <li>10% - Administration and operations</li>
                <li>5% - Research and development</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Giving Options:</h4>
            <div class="grid grid--2" style="margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;">
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>One-Time Gift</h5>
                    <p>Make an immediate impact with a single donation of any amount.</p>
                    <button class="btn">Donate Now</button>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>Monthly Partner</h5>
                    <p>Provide sustained support through automatic monthly giving.</p>
                    <button class="btn">Become a Partner</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h4>Other Ways to Give:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Stock Donations:</strong> Transfer appreciated securities</li>
                <li><strong>Planned Giving:</strong> Include us in your estate planning</li>
                <li><strong>Corporate Matching:</strong> Double your impact through employer programs</li>
                <li><strong>Cryptocurrency:</strong> We accept Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other major cryptocurrencies</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><em>Christian Alms Outreach is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization. All donations are tax-deductible to the extent allowed by law.</em></p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
